  ​  <releases>
        <release version="0.7.0" date="2018-03-22">
            <description>
        ​        <p>New in this version are:
                    <li>Load data from cache file when no connect</li>
                    <li>Add some comments when user select built-in API key</li>
                    <li>Add more information to indicator</li>
                    <li>Add new translations</li>
                    <li>Use GeoClue2 to get location, for Juno support</li>
                </p>
                <p>Fixed issues:
                    <li>#49: wind speed map disappears in Dark Sky mode in flatpak</li>
                    <li>#50: Load from cache when no connect</li>
                    <li>#52: Clicking "Maps" before entering API key breaks the app</li>
                    <li>#53: API key prompt is never explained</li>
                    <li>#57: Please add some of the weather data into the indicator icon</li>
                    <li>#58: Encoding</li>
                    <li>#60: Error saving location to GSettings</li>
                    <li>#61: Use GeoClue2 to get location</li>
                </p>
            </description>
        </release>
